title: Kurt Seligmann Exotic Garden Tie
description:
Tie developed from Kurt Seligmann’s Exotic garden, 1954, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

The sumptuous colors that appear on this unique silk tie were inspired by Exotic garden (c. 1954), a delightful, dreamlike vision of nature by surrealist painter Kurt Seligmann (American, b. Switzerland, 1900-1962). Made in Italy. 

  • Dimensions: 55 in.
  • Material: Silk.
  • Dry clean only.
